; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">MELHOR ATRIZ DE SCI-FI</span></strong></p>  <ul><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">Milla Jovovich: Resident Evil ‚Äì O Recome√ßo</span></li></ul>    <strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">MELHOR ATOR DE SCI-FI</span></strong><ul><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">Matt Smith: Doutor Who</span></li></ul>  <p style="line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">MELHOR ATRIZ DE HORROR</span></strong></p>  <ul><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">Chloe      Grace Moretz: Deixa-Me Entrar</span></li></ul>  <p style="line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">MELHOR ATOR DE HORROR</span></strong></p>  <ul><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">Alexander Skargard: True Blood</span></li></ul>  <p style="line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">MELHOR VILAO</span></strong></p>  <ul><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">Lorde      Voldermort ( Ralph Fiennes ): Harry Potter e as Reliquias da Morte ‚Äì Parte      2</span></li></ul>  <p style="line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">MELHOR SUPER-HEROI</span></strong></p>  <ul><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">Capit√£o  