imes New Roman'',''serif''">MELHOR ELENCO</span></strong></p>  <ul><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">True Blood</span></li></ul>  <p style="line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">MUTILA√á√ÉO MAIS MEMOR√ÅVEL</span></strong></p>  <ul><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">Escalpelado      por barco a motor ‚Äì Piranha 3D</span></li></ul>  <p style="line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">CENA DE LUTA DO ANO</span></strong></p>  <ul><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">A      batalha final : Scott Pilgrin e Knives contra Gideon Graves ‚Äì Scott      Pilgrim Contra o Mundo</span></li></ul>    <strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">A CENA PQP DO ANO</span></strong><ul><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">O      quarto ‚Äì Harry Potter e as Reliquias da Morte ‚Äì Parte 2</span></li></ul>  <p style="line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">MELHOR FILME INDEPENDENTE</span></strong></p>  <ul><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">Monsters</span></li></ul>  <p style="line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">MELHOR FILME 3D</span></strong></p>  <ul><li class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''">Transformers:      O L