re Losing Everything)</em></li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style: disc;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">Helium</em></li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style: disc;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">Pit√§√§k√∂ Mun Kaikki Hoitaa? (Do I Have to Take Care of Everything?)</em></li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style: disc;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">The Voorman Problem</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">Melhor edi√ß√£o de som</strong></p>\r\n<ul style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;">\r\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style: disc;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">At√© o Fim</em></li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style: disc;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">Capit√£o Phillips</em></li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style: disc;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">Gravidade</em></li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style: disc;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">O Hobbit - A Desola√ß√£o de Smaug</em></li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style: disc;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">O Grande Her√≥i</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">Melhor mixagem de som</strong></p>\r\n<ul style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;">\r\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style: disc;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">Capit√£o Phillips</em></li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style: disc;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">Gravidade</em></li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style: disc;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">O Hobbit - A Desola√ß√£o de Smaug</em></li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style: disc;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">Inside Llewin Davis: Balada de um Homem Comum</em></li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style: disc;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">O Grande Her√≥i</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">Melhores efeitos visuais</strong></p>\r\n<ul style="margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px;">\r\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; list-style: disc;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">Gravidade</em></li>\r\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 15px;