as : The Culture Series - Iain Banks</p>\r\n<p>84 - A Caverna de Cristal - Mary Stewart</p>\r\n<p>85 - Anathem - Neal Stephenson</p>\r\n<p>86 - Furies of Calderon : The Codex Alera Series - Jim Butcher</p>\r\n<p>87 - Shadow &amp; Claw : The Book Of The New Sun - Gene Wolfe</p>\r\n<p>88 - Star Wars A Trilogia Thrawn - Timothy Zahn</p>\r\n<p>89 - Outlander : The Outlander Series - Diana Gabaldon</p>\r\n<p>90 - Elric of Melnibone : The Elric Saga - Michael Moorcock</p>\r\n<p>91 - Uma Sombra Passou Por Aqui - Ray Bradbury</p>\r\n<p>92 - Sunshine - Robin McKinley</p>\r\n<p>93 - A Fire upon the Deep - Vernor Vinge</p>\r\n<p>94 - As Cavernas de A√ßo - Isaac Asimov</p>\r\n<p>95 - Red Mars : The Mars Trilogy - Kim Stanley Robinson</p>\r\n<p>96 - Lucifer\\''s Hammer - Larry Niven e Jerry Pournelle</p>\r\n<p>97 - Doomsday Book - Connie Willis</p>\r\n<p>98 - Perdido Street Station - China Mieville</p>\r\n<p>99 - A Spell for Chameleon : The Xanth Series - Piers Anthony</p>\r\n<p>100 - A Trilogia Espacial - C.S. Lewis</p>\r\n<p>¬†</p>', 1, 12, '2015-03-31 05:09:37', 71, 'Findreans ( Eduardo Castelhano )', '2015-04-02 21:26:28', 71, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-03-31 02:06:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, '', 4, 11, '', '', '', 1, 1769);
